name: (1) Ticket for The Melting Pot
description:
Mary Jane's Closet presents: The Melting Pot, a showcase displaying all mediums of art. All artwork, fashion designs and performances will be by young, upcoming artists.

January 10, 2014 6-8 PM
417 N. 8th St. Philadelphia, PA 19123

This is a dressy-casual event. Food and beverages will be served. Come out and enjoy this eventful night with us! This will be a night to remember!

#TheMeltingPotArtExpo


*There will not be any shipping applied to online ticket purchase. We will have a list with names and emails to verify purchase at the door the night of the event. There is also the option of paying at the door.*
